{
  "stem": "1733.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The card told me that she's doing well, not to worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And hopefully, we will be able to see each other soon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this thought, that my mother is there, in Germany, made me feel that I feel-- I felt like going into Germany to find out what happened to my friends, what happened to my girlfriend, Etta, who is my wife, and my parents, and their parents, and what happened to any of the Jews that took-- they took away from home.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on a march from Budapest to Hegyeshalom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hegyeshalom was the town bordering the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know you would like me to spell Hegyeshalom, so I'll spell it for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's H-E-G-Y-E-S capital H-O-L-M-- H-O-L-O-M.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that march, we encountered-- [SIGHS] I have a blank-- blank in my name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Sweden, the diplomat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wallenberg?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Wallenberg was handing out papers, Swedish citizenship papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now any of the kids that received-- that got those papers were not let in into Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were denied entry into Germany by the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he saved a lot of Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not want to take any paper from him, because I wanted to go into Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the reason I wanted to go into Germany is to find out how my mother is doing, how everybody is doing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I worked in the office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were-- and a day before they turned us over to the Germans, at the border, we were working on legal documents made out between the Hungarian government and the German government, listing everybody that was turned over to Germany.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That the-- the Hungarian government is turning over x amount of workers to the German government.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
